item.title: What does thermostat wait mean
item.description: How do I get my Honeywell thermostat off wait? First, turn off your thermostat and HVAC equipment. Then locate then controls for your equipment and switch them off. Wait for a few moments (10-30 seconds) before turning them back on, in reverse order. Why does my thermostat says Cool wait? The Honeywell thermostat system says wait on cool when it is prolonging an activation of your HVAC system. Most commonly, this is done to protect the HVAC system compressor.
